data.description: Introducing your ideal retreat in the prestigious Kitts Creek neighborhood! This stunning home offers the epitome of convenience and luxury with a main-floor master suite, expansive bonus room, granite counters, and stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. Enjoy privacy in the fenced backyard and relax on the screened porch surrounded by gorgeous landscaping. Positioned directly across from the community pool, clubhouse, and fitness center, every amenity is at your doorstep. With a prime location near major transportation hubs and world-class amenities, this home embodies both comfort and elegance. Freshly painted interior 3/24. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever oasis!
